1
00:00:01,250 --> 00:00:02,370
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

2
00:00:10,339 --> 00:00:11,499
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

3
00:00:13,810 --> 00:00:15,745
<Default><b>I can't believe
what I'm seeing here!</b></Default>

4
00:00:15,769 --> 00:00:18,480
<Default><b>The Topak family
already has Team Rockvalley</b></Default>

5
00:00:18,559 --> 00:00:20,319
<Default><b>fighting for
their lives!</b></Default>

6
00:00:21,149 --> 00:00:22,820
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

7
00:00:22,980 --> 00:00:24,060
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

8
00:00:24,690 --> 00:00:25,970
<Default><b>[uneasy gasp]</b></Default>

9
00:00:26,399 --> 00:00:28,675
<Default><b>Hah! And here I thought
they'd be tougher.</b></Default>

10
00:00:28,699 --> 00:00:29,925
<Default><b>Guess I was wrong.</b></Default>

11
00:00:29,949 --> 00:00:31,949
<Default><b>C'mon let's
finish them all off!</b></Default>

12
00:00:32,530 --> 00:00:34,095
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
It's looking grim!</b></Default>

13
00:00:34,119 --> 00:00:37,239
<Default><b>Will Team Rockvalley be able
to fight their way out of this?</b></Default>

14
00:00:37,960 --> 00:00:39,329
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

15
00:00:39,869 --> 00:00:41,265
<Default><b>[menacing laughter]</b></Default>

16
00:00:41,289 --> 00:00:42,369
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

17
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:46,160
<Default><b>[crashing]</b></Default>

18
00:00:48,130 --> 00:00:49,330
<Default><b>[exploding]</b></Default>

19
00:00:49,380 --> 00:00:53,390
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

20
00:02:32,569 --> 00:02:34,769
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
My name is Naofumi Iwatani.</b></Default>

21
00:02:35,199 --> 00:02:36,756
<Default><b>I was sent from
modern Japan</b></Default>

22
00:02:36,780 --> 00:02:38,716
<Default><b>to another world
as the Shield Hero</b></Default>

23
00:02:38,740 --> 00:02:40,466
<Default><b>in order to
fight the Waves</b></Default>

24
00:02:40,490 --> 00:02:42,850
<Default><b>which bring about
calamity to this world.</b></Default>

25
00:02:43,500 --> 00:02:45,226
<Default><b>But since the
Spirit Tortoise</b></Default>

26
00:02:45,250 --> 00:02:46,855
<Default><b>one of the four
guardian beasts</b></Default>

27
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:49,050
<Default><b>that protect this world</b></Default>

28
00:02:49,129 --> 00:02:51,649
<Default><b>it'll be a while
before another Wave happens.</b></Default>

29
00:02:52,259 --> 00:02:54,605
<Default><b>The guardian beasts
make use of soul energy</b></Default>

30
00:02:54,629 --> 00:02:56,316
<Default><b>gathered by
killing people</b></Default>

31
00:02:56,340 --> 00:02:58,300
<Default><b>to stop the Waves
from coming.</b></Default>

32
00:03:04,939 --> 00:03:06,876
<Default><b>We defeated
the Spirit Tortoise</b></Default>

33
00:03:06,900 --> 00:03:09,310
<Default><b>so the next
Guardian Beast</b></Default>

34
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:11,760
<Default><b>was supposed to revive
immediately after.</b></Default>

35
00:03:13,780 --> 00:03:16,360
<Default><b>Luckily the energy
we took back from Kyo</b></Default>

36
00:03:16,449 --> 00:03:18,925
<Default><b>created a barrier that
gave us three and a half months</b></Default>

37
00:03:18,949 --> 00:03:20,509
<Default><b>before that happens.</b></Default>

38
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:23,260
<Default><b>I plan to use that time</b></Default>

39
00:03:23,289 --> 00:03:25,436
<Default><b>to strengthen
the defenses of my lands</b></Default>

40
00:03:25,460 --> 00:03:28,169
<Default><b>and make preparations
to defeat the Phoenix.</b></Default>

41
00:03:28,789 --> 00:03:30,566
<Default><b>But because
of the sacrifice aura</b></Default>

42
00:03:30,590 --> 00:03:32,919
<Default><b>put on us during
my fight with Kyo.</b></Default>

43
00:03:33,090 --> 00:03:34,730
<Default><b>Raphtalia, Filo, and I</b></Default>

44
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:38,009
<Default><b>all took a big hit to our stats
that can't be overlooked.</b></Default>

45
00:03:38,139 --> 00:03:39,339
<Default><b>[crackling]</b></Default>

46
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:43,270
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Lowhirot, Haikazuya</b></Default>

47
00:03:43,349 --> 00:03:44,430
<Default><b>Mideus.</b></Default>

48
00:03:44,639 --> 00:03:46,115
<Default><b>The armies
gathered to defeat</b></Default>

49
00:03:46,139 --> 00:03:48,259
<Default><b>the Spirit Tortoise
are still here?</b></Default>

50
00:03:49,900 --> 00:03:51,310
<Default><b>And those flags.</b></Default>

51
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,760
<Default><b>That's Faubrey.</b></Default>

52
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:55,216
<Default><b>The Spirit Tortoise
has already been defeated</b></Default>

53
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,120
<Default><b>so what are
they doing here?</b></Default>

54
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:58,756
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
As for the liberation aura</b></Default>

55
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:00,300
<Default><b>that Ost taught me.</b></Default>

56
00:04:00,530 --> 00:04:02,490
<Default><b>I haven't been
able to use it.</b></Default>

57
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:04,460
<Default><b>I don't know
if I ever will.</b></Default>

58
00:04:05,370 --> 00:04:06,596
<Default><b>I'm the Shield.</b></Default>

59
00:04:06,620 --> 00:04:08,180
<Default><b>Motoyasu, the Spear.</b></Default>

60
00:04:08,210 --> 00:04:09,476
<Default><b>Ren, the Sword.</b></Default>

61
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:11,060
<Default><b>And Itsuki, the Bow.</b></Default>

62
00:04:11,129 --> 00:04:12,395
<Default><b>With proper teamwork</b></Default>

63
00:04:12,419 --> 00:04:14,605
<Default><b>our abilities can make
all the difference</b></Default>

64
00:04:14,629 --> 00:04:16,485
<Default><b>in making each
other stronger.</b></Default>

65
00:04:16,509 --> 00:04:18,509
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

66
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:20,826
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What do you mean "Missing"?</b></Default>

67
00:04:20,850 --> 00:04:22,550
<Default><b>Only you remain.</b></Default>

68
00:04:22,639 --> 00:04:23,826
<Default><b>The other three heroes</b></Default>

69
00:04:23,850 --> 00:04:26,286
<Default><b>dealt with the Wave that
took place after you left</b></Default>

70
00:04:26,310 --> 00:04:28,245
<Default><b>for the other world
and vanished.</b></Default>

71
00:04:28,269 --> 00:04:29,915
<Default><b>Right, that was the wave
that occurred</b></Default>

72
00:04:29,939 --> 00:04:31,536
<Default><b>alongside the
one Kyo created</b></Default>

73
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,165
<Default><b>if I'm remembering
correctly.</b></Default>

74
00:04:33,189 --> 00:04:35,669
<Default><b>We were all grateful to them
for their help.</b></Default>

75
00:04:36,029 --> 00:04:38,989
<Default><b>But it's likely they felt
responsible for what happened.</b></Default>

76
00:04:39,069 --> 00:04:41,175
<Default><b>[MIRELIA]
Because now they're missing.</b></Default>

77
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:42,919
<Default><b>You gotta be kidding me.</b></Default>

78
00:04:42,949 --> 00:04:45,096
<Default><b>[MIRELIA]
With the Phoenix soon to revive</b></Default>

79
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,096
<Default><b>having even one of the heroes
absent</b></Default>

80
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:49,459
<Default><b>would be an extremely
serious concern</b></Default>

81
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:51,516
<Default><b>given the circumstances
we're in.</b></Default>

82
00:04:51,540 --> 00:04:52,580
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

83
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:55,050
<Default><b>I pity the citizens
of this land.</b></Default>

84
00:04:55,589 --> 00:04:58,065
<Default><b>First, the Waves of Catastrophe
loom over them</b></Default>

85
00:04:58,089 --> 00:04:59,849
<Default><b>now, the
guardian beasts.</b></Default>

86
00:05:00,220 --> 00:05:01,589
<Default><b>Sir Naofumi</b></Default>

87
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:03,319
<Default><b>I surrender my pride</b></Default>

88
00:05:03,389 --> 00:05:05,326
<Default><b>and request you
to lend us your aid</b></Default>

89
00:05:05,350 --> 00:05:07,310
<Default><b>once more as
the Shield Hero.</b></Default>

90
00:05:08,230 --> 00:05:09,915
<Default><b>There's no
need for that.</b></Default>

91
00:05:09,939 --> 00:05:12,739
<Default><b>I'll fight to protect my lands
no matter the threat.</b></Default>

92
00:05:12,769 --> 00:05:14,536
<Default><b>But what do
you plan to do?</b></Default>

93
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,836
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Nations like Faubrey</b></Default>

94
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:17,836
<Default><b>are snooping around
your country.</b></Default>

95
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:20,125
<Default><b>Am I wrong in thinking
the Queen of Melromarc</b></Default>

96
00:05:20,149 --> 00:05:22,149
<Default><b>should be
concerned about that?</b></Default>

97
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:25,029
<Default><b>Faubrey stationed
their soldiers nearby</b></Default>

98
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:27,096
<Default><b>in what they're calling
a "relief effort</b></Default>"

99
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:29,400
<Default><b>after you defeated
the Spirit Tortoise.</b></Default>

100
00:05:29,699 --> 00:05:32,920
<Default><b>So the Eastern nations are
merely keeping them in check.</b></Default>

101
00:05:33,170 --> 00:05:35,226
<Default><b>I'd say there's
nothing to worry about</b></Default>

102
00:05:35,250 --> 00:05:37,709
<Default><b>since Melromarc
and Faubrey are allies.</b></Default>

103
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:40,200
<Default><b>[MIRELIA]
At least, for the time being.</b></Default>

104
00:05:40,420 --> 00:05:44,430
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

105
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:46,310
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

106
00:05:46,509 --> 00:05:47,549
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

107
00:05:48,350 --> 00:05:50,110
<Default><b>[FILO]
Hey look! It's Mel!</b></Default>

108
00:05:50,139 --> 00:05:51,179
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

109
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,980
<Default><b>Goodness, grief.</b></Default>

110
00:05:56,069 --> 00:05:57,769
<Default><b>It's been so long!</b></Default>

111
00:05:57,899 --> 00:05:59,059
<Default><b>[giggling]</b></Default>

112
00:05:59,149 --> 00:06:01,069
<Default><b>It's good to
see you, Filo!</b></Default>

113
00:06:01,569 --> 00:06:03,319
<Default><b>My apologies, Raphtalia.</b></Default>

114
00:06:03,410 --> 00:06:04,069
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

115
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:06,005
<Default><b>Our nation's
religion dictates</b></Default>

116
00:06:06,029 --> 00:06:07,846
<Default><b>that we worship
the four heroes now.</b></Default>

117
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:09,976
<Default><b>But there are still
a lot of people out there</b></Default>

118
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:12,370
<Default><b>who don't like
Naofumi or Demi-humans.</b></Default>

119
00:06:12,459 --> 00:06:14,870
<Default><b>It's fine.
They'll come around eventually.</b></Default>

120
00:06:14,959 --> 00:06:17,185
<Default><b>Mother wants them dismissed
from their positions</b></Default>

121
00:06:17,209 --> 00:06:19,526
<Default><b>but they were some of my
father's most trusted men</b></Default>

122
00:06:19,550 --> 00:06:22,170
<Default><b>which complicates things
to say the very least.</b></Default>

123
00:06:22,509 --> 00:06:24,429
<Default><b>Nothing's ever
simple, is it?</b></Default>

124
00:06:24,680 --> 00:06:26,300
<Default><b>[sighing]</b></Default>

125
00:06:27,100 --> 00:06:29,759
<Default><b>What this world calls
the Vassal Weapon Heroes.</b></Default>

126
00:06:30,220 --> 00:06:31,889
<Default><b>The Seven Star Heroes.</b></Default>

127
00:06:32,139 --> 00:06:33,859
<Default><b>Any idea where they are?</b></Default>

128
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:36,536
<Default><b>They should all be somewhere
out there in the world.</b></Default>

129
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:39,980
<Default><b>The only problem is
we can't contact most of them.</b></Default>

130
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,899
<Default><b>Yeah, and why's that?</b></Default>

131
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:44,216
<Default><b>We've tried
to track them all down</b></Default>

132
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:47,120
<Default><b>but we've yet to come across
any decent leads.</b></Default>

133
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:54,579
<Default><b>That is</b></Default>

134
00:06:54,910 --> 00:06:57,379
<Default><b>We are keenly aware
of their location.</b></Default>

135
00:06:57,709 --> 00:06:59,420
<Default><b>The staff hero, huh?</b></Default>

136
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:01,589
<Default><b>Okay where are they?</b></Default>

137
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:05,879
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

138
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:12,019
<Default><b>Right here in Melromarc.</b></Default>

139
00:07:12,139 --> 00:07:13,230
<Default><b>What?!</b></Default>

140
00:07:13,639 --> 00:07:15,139
<Default><b>Sir Naofumi.</b></Default>

141
00:07:17,189 --> 00:07:19,319
<Default><b>Could I ask you
to accompany me?</b></Default>

142
00:07:19,810 --> 00:07:22,050
<Default><b>There's something
I'd like you to see.</b></Default>

143
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:25,699
<Default><b>Hey, are you
going somewhere</b></Default>

144
00:07:25,779 --> 00:07:27,819
<Default><b>Yes, I'm off
to Seyaette.</b></Default>

145
00:07:27,949 --> 00:07:31,120
<Default><b>Seyaette? That's near
Master's lands, isn't it?</b></Default>

146
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:32,079
<Default><b>Mmhm.</b></Default>

147
00:07:32,160 --> 00:07:34,476
<Default><b>Wait, that means we can
play again, right? Yay!</b></Default>

148
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:36,579
<Default><b>- Yay!
- [both giggling]</b></Default>

149
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:40,000
<Default><b>Eclair's having a rather
tough time ruling her lands.</b></Default>

150
00:07:40,089 --> 00:07:41,646
<Default><b>So I'm going
to go help her!</b></Default>

151
00:07:41,670 --> 00:07:43,800
<Default><b>You're awfully
busy for a princess.</b></Default>

152
00:07:44,050 --> 00:07:46,220
<Default><b>[MELTY] It's
not just a title</b></Default>

153
00:07:46,379 --> 00:07:48,815
<Default><b>Now, we're going to
finish packing and leave today</b></Default>

154
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,879
<Default><b>so let's get a
move on, everyone!</b></Default>

155
00:07:52,470 --> 00:07:54,639
<Default><b>I daresay</b></Default>

156
00:07:54,970 --> 00:07:56,639
<Default><b>- Hm.
- "Daresay"?</b></Default>

157
00:07:58,269 --> 00:07:59,909
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What is this?</b></Default>

158
00:07:59,980 --> 00:08:03,149
<Default><b>We were able to recover
the Spirit Tortoise's body.</b></Default>

159
00:08:03,730 --> 00:08:05,990
<Default><b>That didn't take
you very long, huh?</b></Default>

160
00:08:06,740 --> 00:08:09,160
<Default><b>[whirring and beeping]</b></Default>

161
00:08:10,990 --> 00:08:13,990
<Default><b>[grunts]
Is this a final gift from Ost?</b></Default>

162
00:08:15,660 --> 00:08:20,629
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

163
00:08:21,579 --> 00:08:23,050
<Default><b>Sir Naofumi</b></Default>

164
00:08:23,379 --> 00:08:26,170
<Default><b>this is very
difficult for me to say but...</b></Default>

165
00:08:26,300 --> 00:08:28,129
<Default><b>Malty...
[clears throat]</b></Default>

166
00:08:28,509 --> 00:08:31,680
<Default><b>I mean Bitch, appears to have
gone missing as well.</b></Default>

167
00:08:32,970 --> 00:08:36,139
<Default><b>I'm told she was last sighted
near the northern border.</b></Default>

168
00:08:36,519 --> 00:08:37,655
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
The north?</b></Default>

169
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,759
<Default><b>[MIRELIA]
Please exercise caution.</b></Default>

170
00:08:40,269 --> 00:08:42,690
<Default><b>As I'm sure you know</b></Default>

171
00:08:42,769 --> 00:08:44,169
<Default><b>- [clatter] Huh?</b></Default>

172
00:08:45,110 --> 00:08:46,296
<Default><b>The Shield Hero?</b></Default>

173
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:48,149
<Default><b>What are you doing here</b></Default>

174
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,400
<Default><b>[exclaims]</b></Default>

175
00:08:50,409 --> 00:08:51,449
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

176
00:08:55,620 --> 00:08:58,330
<Default><b>I can't believe that
he's the Staff Hero.</b></Default>

177
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:02,289
<Default><b>[distant clanging]</b></Default>

178
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:10,879
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

179
00:09:11,259 --> 00:09:12,720
<Default><b>[clanging]</b></Default>

180
00:09:16,389 --> 00:09:17,655
<Default><b>[ELHART]
That you, kid?</b></Default>

181
00:09:17,679 --> 00:09:18,745
<Default><b>In the flesh!</b></Default>

182
00:09:18,769 --> 00:09:20,245
<Default><b>Not too busy are ya?</b></Default>

183
00:09:20,269 --> 00:09:21,429
<Default><b>[giggling]</b></Default>

184
00:09:21,769 --> 00:09:22,929
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

185
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:25,745
<Default><b>[ELHART] I see.</b></Default>

186
00:09:25,769 --> 00:09:27,836
<Default><b>Between the Spirit Tortoise
and that other world</b></Default>

187
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:29,700
<Default><b>you've had
your hands full.</b></Default>

188
00:09:29,779 --> 00:09:30,899
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

189
00:09:37,659 --> 00:09:39,379
<Default><b>- [ELHART] Kid?
- [gasps]</b></Default>

190
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:42,120
<Default><b>Are you okay?
You spaced out there.</b></Default>

191
00:09:42,210 --> 00:09:43,879
<Default><b>Ah, it's nothing.</b></Default>

192
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:45,360
<Default><b>More importantly</b></Default>

193
00:09:45,460 --> 00:09:46,726
<Default><b>about why I'm here.</b></Default>

194
00:09:46,750 --> 00:09:48,230
<Default><b>We need your help.</b></Default>

195
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:50,145
<Default><b>- Mmhm.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

196
00:09:50,169 --> 00:09:52,275
<Default><b>I used this gear
in the other world</b></Default>

197
00:09:52,299 --> 00:09:54,655
<Default><b>but haven't been able
to use it since then.</b></Default>

198
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:56,429
<Default><b>Hmmm. Sure is strange.</b></Default>

199
00:09:56,509 --> 00:09:57,826
<Default><b>What is this stuff?</b></Default>

200
00:09:57,850 --> 00:10:00,370
<Default><b>Is something wrong?
With the gear I have now?</b></Default>

201
00:10:00,429 --> 00:10:03,149
<Default><b>No, I just liked
how you looked in it.</b></Default>

202
00:10:03,649 --> 00:10:06,369
<Default><b>Not to mention, your stats
were higher in it, too.</b></Default>

203
00:10:06,769 --> 00:10:08,125
<Default><b>I'll see what I can do.</b></Default>

204
00:10:08,149 --> 00:10:10,389
<Default><b>But I bet I can get it
working for ya.</b></Default>

205
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:12,375
<Default><b>Can you get it
working for cheap?</b></Default>

206
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:14,279
<Default><b>Damn. Stingy
as ever, huh?</b></Default>

207
00:10:14,370 --> 00:10:16,216
<Default><b>How's this?
You come to my lands</b></Default>

208
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,926
<Default><b>and sell your weapons
there instead?</b></Default>

209
00:10:17,950 --> 00:10:20,426
<Default><b>Oh, so you can work me
harder than you do here?</b></Default>

210
00:10:20,450 --> 00:10:21,976
<Default><b>I don't think so, kid.</b></Default>

211
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:24,265
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] What if I paid you
30 silvers a month?</b></Default>

212
00:10:24,289 --> 00:10:26,515
<Default><b>[ELHART] What if I told you
I make more than that?</b></Default>

213
00:10:26,539 --> 00:10:29,099
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] 25 it is!
[ELHART] That's even less!</b></Default>

214
00:10:31,419 --> 00:10:35,929
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

215
00:10:36,139 --> 00:10:39,035
<Default><b>They've officially switched
to worshiping the Four Heroes</b></Default>

216
00:10:39,059 --> 00:10:41,899
<Default><b>but I guess people don't change
that easily, do they?</b></Default>

217
00:10:41,980 --> 00:10:44,206
<Default><b>[RISHIA] Change doesn't
happen overnight.</b></Default>

218
00:10:44,230 --> 00:10:45,826
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Melty's ideal country</b></Default>

219
00:10:45,850 --> 00:10:47,330
<Default><b>is a long way off.</b></Default>

220
00:10:48,019 --> 00:10:50,320
<Default><b>Ah, it's been
far too long</b></Default>

221
00:10:50,399 --> 00:10:52,190
<Default><b>Shield Hero!</b></Default>

222
00:10:52,279 --> 00:10:53,836
<Default><b>But I had a feeling
you'd be showing</b></Default>

223
00:10:53,860 --> 00:10:55,836
<Default><b>your face around here
sooner or later!</b></Default>

224
00:10:55,860 --> 00:10:57,870
<Default><b>- Is this all?
- Hmm.</b></Default>

225
00:10:58,200 --> 00:11:00,096
<Default><b>There's barely
any slaves here.</b></Default>

226
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,426
<Default><b>There a reason for that?</b></Default>

227
00:11:01,450 --> 00:11:04,659
<Default><b>My, do you really not know
what's been happening?</b></Default>

228
00:11:04,870 --> 00:11:07,500
<Default><b>News of you reuniting
the scattered villagers</b></Default>

229
00:11:07,590 --> 00:11:11,340
<Default><b>of Lurolona Village
from a certain "source"</b></Default>

230
00:11:11,460 --> 00:11:13,460
<Default><b>has already made
its way around.</b></Default>

231
00:11:13,549 --> 00:11:16,129
<Default><b>Damn it, this has to be
the Queen's doing.</b></Default>

232
00:11:16,759 --> 00:11:19,239
<Default><b>I figured if I was going
to improve my lands</b></Default>

233
00:11:19,309 --> 00:11:20,655
<Default><b>it would be
easier to do it</b></Default>

234
00:11:20,679 --> 00:11:22,405
<Default><b>with the people
who had lived there before.</b></Default>

235
00:11:22,429 --> 00:11:24,416
<Default><b>Well, unfortunately
for you, my friend</b></Default>

236
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:26,666
<Default><b>the nobles and merchants
caught wind of your plan</b></Default>

237
00:11:26,690 --> 00:11:28,666
<Default><b>so they went ahead
and decided to buy up</b></Default>

238
00:11:28,690 --> 00:11:30,166
<Default><b>all the slaves
from the village</b></Default>

239
00:11:30,190 --> 00:11:31,796
<Default><b>to sell outside
the country.</b></Default>

240
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:33,875
<Default><b>How much would it cost
to buy them back?</b></Default>

241
00:11:33,899 --> 00:11:36,659
<Default><b>At the moment</b></Default>

242
00:11:36,820 --> 00:11:39,620
<Default><b>I would say around
30 gold a head.</b></Default>

243
00:11:40,029 --> 00:11:42,990
<Default><b>I only paid 30 silvers
when I got Raphtalia!</b></Default>

244
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:45,265
<Default><b>[gasps] So it's a 100 times
her price?</b></Default>

245
00:11:45,289 --> 00:11:47,629
<Default><b>It was actually
31 silvers.</b></Default>

246
00:11:47,710 --> 00:11:49,686
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Why is the price so high now?</b></Default>

247
00:11:49,710 --> 00:11:51,789
<Default><b>Sorry, friend</b></Default>

248
00:11:51,879 --> 00:11:54,316
<Default><b>You never know which way
Lady Fortune is gonna swing!</b></Default>

249
00:11:54,340 --> 00:11:55,395
<Default><b>Okay fine.</b></Default>

250
00:11:55,419 --> 00:11:58,275
<Default><b>Then I'll go ahead and buy
every slave that's left here.</b></Default>

251
00:11:58,299 --> 00:12:01,019
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] So give me
all the information you have.</b></Default>

252
00:12:01,429 --> 00:12:04,100
<Default><b>And this is exactly
why I do so love</b></Default>

253
00:12:04,179 --> 00:12:06,155
<Default><b>doing business
with you, Shield Hero!</b></Default>

254
00:12:06,179 --> 00:12:08,559
<Default><b>If the Demi-humans
from Lurolona Village</b></Default>

255
00:12:08,649 --> 00:12:10,249
<Default><b>are the ones you seek</b></Default>

256
00:12:10,519 --> 00:12:13,940
<Default><b>then I'd start planning a trip
to Zeltoble if I were you.</b></Default>

257
00:12:14,779 --> 00:12:16,240
<Default><b>To Zeltoble?</b></Default>

258
00:12:18,990 --> 00:12:21,176
<Default><b>Do you really have
to leave for Zeltoble</b></Default>

259
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,716
<Default><b>after you just got back?</b></Default>

260
00:12:22,740 --> 00:12:25,176
<Default><b>Seeing as the other three heroes
have gone missing</b></Default>

261
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:27,096
<Default><b>I'm gonna need to
find a lot more people</b></Default>

262
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,556
<Default><b>to help me
defend my lands.</b></Default>

263
00:12:28,580 --> 00:12:29,895
<Default><b>Hey, why don't
you just use that</b></Default>

264
00:12:29,919 --> 00:12:32,145
<Default><b>portal thing of yours
instead of the carriage?</b></Default>

265
00:12:32,169 --> 00:12:33,645
<Default><b>In order to
warp somewhere</b></Default>

266
00:12:33,669 --> 00:12:35,605
<Default><b>you have to have
been there before.</b></Default>

267
00:12:35,629 --> 00:12:37,970
<Default><b>Hm... That's a bummer.</b></Default>

268
00:12:38,049 --> 00:12:39,365
<Default><b>I'd be happy
to look after</b></Default>

269
00:12:39,389 --> 00:12:41,629
<Default><b>all the Demi-human
slaves you brought.</b></Default>

270
00:12:41,759 --> 00:12:43,615
<Default><b>[MELTY]
Eclair, Elrasla, and I</b></Default>

271
00:12:43,639 --> 00:12:45,905
<Default><b>will teach them everything
they need to know.</b></Default>

272
00:12:45,929 --> 00:12:47,155
<Default><b>[KEEL]
And as their superior</b></Default>

273
00:12:47,179 --> 00:12:49,139
<Default><b>I'll train 'em
to be the best!</b></Default>

274
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:50,875
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
All right. I'm counting on you.</b></Default>

275
00:12:50,899 --> 00:12:52,706
<Default><b>[FILO]
Bye, Mel, see you later!</b></Default>

276
00:12:52,730 --> 00:12:54,336
<Default><b>[MELTY]
Take care, everyone!</b></Default>

277
00:12:54,360 --> 00:13:01,370
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

278
00:13:43,490 --> 00:13:45,426
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
There it is, everyone!</b></Default>

279
00:13:45,450 --> 00:13:46,885
<Default><b>On the other side
of that bridge</b></Default>

280
00:13:46,909 --> 00:13:49,189
<Default><b>- is the capital of Zeltoble.
- [gasps]</b></Default>

281
00:13:49,830 --> 00:13:52,110
<Default><b>A country of merchants
and mercenaries.</b></Default>

282
00:13:52,210 --> 00:13:54,306
<Default><b>- There's so much here.
- [exclaiming]</b></Default>

283
00:13:54,330 --> 00:13:56,039
<Default><b>There's even an arena.</b></Default>

284
00:13:56,500 --> 00:13:58,100
<Default><b>This place is packed.</b></Default>

285
00:13:58,299 --> 00:13:59,895
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
And so lively, too!</b></Default>

286
00:13:59,919 --> 00:14:02,239
<Default><b>[FILO] I hope
they have tasty food here!</b></Default>

287
00:14:02,629 --> 00:14:06,100
<Default><b>So, where's the shop that the
Slave Merchant told us about?</b></Default>

288
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:09,785
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
This is it?</b></Default>

289
00:14:09,809 --> 00:14:11,865
<Default><b>It's smaller than
I thought it'd be.</b></Default>

290
00:14:11,889 --> 00:14:13,649
<Default><b>And it's also a tavern?</b></Default>

291
00:14:14,149 --> 00:14:16,820
<Default><b>He said we'd understand
when we got here but...</b></Default>

292
00:14:17,269 --> 00:14:18,336
<Default><b>Hello hello!</b></Default>

293
00:14:18,360 --> 00:14:20,466
<Default><b>I take it you're
the Shield Hero, yes?</b></Default>

294
00:14:20,490 --> 00:14:23,125
<Default><b>My, what a pleasure to
finally meet you, kind sir.</b></Default>

295
00:14:23,149 --> 00:14:25,426
<Default><b>[FILO] Huh? Wait.
What's he doing here?</b></Default>

296
00:14:25,450 --> 00:14:28,159
<Default><b>Ho-hooo!
I like the look in your eyes.</b></Default>

297
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:29,806
<Default><b>Just like my
nephew said.</b></Default>

298
00:14:29,830 --> 00:14:31,306
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
Such a fiery streak</b></Default>

299
00:14:31,330 --> 00:14:32,596
<Default><b>of determination!</b></Default>

300
00:14:32,620 --> 00:14:35,500
<Default><b>Anyway, I'm one of the local
slave merchants</b></Default>

301
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:37,066
<Default><b>stationed here
in Zeltoble.</b></Default>

302
00:14:37,090 --> 00:14:39,879
<Default><b>My nephew says you're
one of his best customers.</b></Default>

303
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:41,920
<Default><b>Now please,
come in, come in.</b></Default>

304
00:14:45,889 --> 00:14:47,115
<Default><b>In this country</b></Default>

305
00:14:47,139 --> 00:14:49,326
<Default><b>there are many places
above the surface</b></Default>

306
00:14:49,350 --> 00:14:51,929
<Default><b>where you can
have fun, but...</b></Default>

307
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:54,240
<Default><b>The real fun to be had</b></Default>

308
00:14:54,269 --> 00:14:56,269
<Default><b>in this country
lies beneath it.</b></Default>

309
00:14:57,190 --> 00:14:58,310
<Default><b>[sliding]</b></Default>

310
00:15:00,649 --> 00:15:02,089
<Default><b>[cabinet sliding]</b></Default>

311
00:15:02,440 --> 00:15:04,296
<Default><b>These underground
staircases</b></Default>

312
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:06,990
<Default><b>can be found all
throughout Zeltoble.</b></Default>

313
00:15:07,070 --> 00:15:09,409
<Default><b>Each one leads to
a spectacular place</b></Default>

314
00:15:09,490 --> 00:15:12,370
<Default><b>full of fun, excitement</b></Default>

315
00:15:13,330 --> 00:15:15,539
<Default><b>You're a lucky one</b></Default>

316
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:17,605
<Default><b>I heard rumors that
what you're looking for</b></Default>

317
00:15:17,629 --> 00:15:19,840
<Default><b>just so happened
to come in today.</b></Default>

318
00:15:20,549 --> 00:15:22,485
<Default><b>[AUCTIONEER 01-A (M)]
Now, our next item</b></Default>

319
00:15:22,509 --> 00:15:24,109
<Default><b>from Lurolona Village</b></Default>

320
00:15:24,169 --> 00:15:26,889
<Default><b>which is now owned
by the Shield Hero</b></Default>

321
00:15:27,009 --> 00:15:28,600
<Default><b>a Demi-human!</b></Default>

322
00:15:29,179 --> 00:15:32,019
<Default><b>Is this some kind of underworld
auction or something?</b></Default>

323
00:15:32,269 --> 00:15:34,245
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
Yes. You can buy things here</b></Default>

324
00:15:34,269 --> 00:15:35,535
<Default><b>you can't on the surface</b></Default>

325
00:15:35,559 --> 00:15:38,326
<Default><b>like the slaves whose ownership
is forbade in Melromarc</b></Default>

326
00:15:38,350 --> 00:15:40,070
<Default><b>being sold here tonight.</b></Default>

327
00:15:43,070 --> 00:15:44,716
<Default><b>Hello, nice to
meet you all!</b></Default>

328
00:15:44,740 --> 00:15:47,005
<Default><b>I'm a Demi-human from
Lurolona Village!</b></Default>

329
00:15:47,029 --> 00:15:48,320
<Default><b>She's lying.</b></Default>

330
00:15:48,909 --> 00:15:50,846
<Default><b>[AUCTIONEER 01-A (M)]
We'll start the bidding at 50.</b></Default>

331
00:15:50,870 --> 00:15:52,830
<Default><b>I see 60 in the crowd.</b></Default>

332
00:15:52,909 --> 00:15:54,330
<Default><b>65.</b></Default>

333
00:15:54,580 --> 00:15:55,789
<Default><b>68.</b></Default>

334
00:15:56,289 --> 00:15:57,539
<Default><b>69.</b></Default>

335
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,129
<Default><b>72.</b></Default>

336
00:15:59,590 --> 00:16:00,590
<Default><b>75.</b></Default>

337
00:16:01,419 --> 00:16:03,509
<Default><b>I know your intentions
were good</b></Default>

338
00:16:03,590 --> 00:16:06,470
<Default><b>but this is the result of your
endeavors to save them.</b></Default>

339
00:16:06,879 --> 00:16:08,379
<Default><b>But, hey</b></Default>

340
00:16:08,470 --> 00:16:11,430
<Default><b>You never know which way
Lady Fortune is going to swing.</b></Default>

341
00:16:11,679 --> 00:16:14,076
<Default><b>[AUCTIONEER 01-A (M)]
Could it be? Do I see 100?!</b></Default>

342
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:15,140
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

343
00:16:15,220 --> 00:16:16,580
<Default><b>[crowd gasping]</b></Default>

344
00:16:17,769 --> 00:16:19,745
<Default><b>The gentleman
with sign number 14</b></Default>

345
00:16:19,769 --> 00:16:21,940
<Default><b>has won
with a bid of one hundred!</b></Default>

346
00:16:22,230 --> 00:16:24,149
<Default><b>[gasps]
A-a hundred?</b></Default>

347
00:16:24,230 --> 00:16:25,990
<Default><b>Thank you
very much, sir.</b></Default>

348
00:16:26,700 --> 00:16:29,909
<Default><b>You have my word that I will do
my very best to serve you.</b></Default>

349
00:16:30,029 --> 00:16:31,096
<Default><b>That girl</b></Default>

350
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:33,400
<Default><b>she's not really
from Lurolona Village.</b></Default>

351
00:16:33,580 --> 00:16:36,226
<Default><b>Well, it doesn't matter
where she's actually from.</b></Default>

352
00:16:36,250 --> 00:16:38,330
<Default><b>The appeal
of the Lurolona "brand"</b></Default>

353
00:16:38,409 --> 00:16:39,726
<Default><b>the Shield Hero created</b></Default>

354
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:41,550
<Default><b>is too powerful
to resist!</b></Default>

355
00:16:41,919 --> 00:16:43,145
<Default><b>[RISHIA]
But that's...</b></Default>

356
00:16:43,169 --> 00:16:44,605
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]
Ridiculous, you think?</b></Default>

357
00:16:44,629 --> 00:16:45,895
<Default><b>Impossible even?</b></Default>

358
00:16:45,919 --> 00:16:47,485
<Default><b>Ah, but you
see, my child</b></Default>

359
00:16:47,509 --> 00:16:50,429
<Default><b>all things are possible
when money is involved!</b></Default>

360
00:16:50,639 --> 00:16:52,359
<Default><b>It makes the world turn!</b></Default>

361
00:16:53,259 --> 00:16:55,499
<Default><b>Seems like tonight
was a bust for you.</b></Default>

362
00:16:55,809 --> 00:16:57,405
<Default><b>But I have solid info</b></Default>

363
00:16:57,429 --> 00:16:59,509
<Default><b>that a Lurolona Village
Demi-human</b></Default>

364
00:16:59,559 --> 00:17:00,959
<Default><b>is in this city.</b></Default>

365
00:17:01,190 --> 00:17:02,769
<Default><b>Say, Shield Hero</b></Default>

366
00:17:03,110 --> 00:17:05,590
<Default><b>how much money
do you have on you right now?</b></Default>

367
00:17:06,029 --> 00:17:07,400
<Default><b>A hundred gold?</b></Default>

368
00:17:07,859 --> 00:17:09,740
<Default><b>No, 50 gold perhaps?</b></Default>

369
00:17:09,819 --> 00:17:11,386
<Default><b>What are you getting at?</b></Default>

370
00:17:11,410 --> 00:17:14,130
<Default><b>A little birdy told me
you spent quite the fortune</b></Default>

371
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:16,369
<Default><b>buying all the
slaves in Melromarc.</b></Default>

372
00:17:16,910 --> 00:17:19,265
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)]If only
you saved some of your money.</b></Default>

373
00:17:19,289 --> 00:17:21,500
<Default><b>How terribly
tragic for you.</b></Default>

374
00:17:22,250 --> 00:17:23,726
<Default><b>- [AUCTIONEER] Now, on to our next...
- [NAOFUMI] I'm guessing</b></Default>

375
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:24,815
<Default><b>you have an idea</b></Default>

376
00:17:24,839 --> 00:17:25,896
<Default><b>how I can earn
some money?</b></Default>

377
00:17:25,920 --> 00:17:26,759
<Default><b>[AUCTIONEER] You're gonna
love this one!</b></Default>

378
00:17:26,839 --> 00:17:29,235
<Default><b>You've never seen anything
like it before![Laughing]</b></Default>

379
00:17:29,259 --> 00:17:31,525
<Default><b>[SLAVE MERCHANT 01-B (M)] You
saw the coliseum earlier, right?</b></Default>

380
00:17:31,549 --> 00:17:33,575
<Default><b>People in there
fight fair and square</b></Default>

381
00:17:33,599 --> 00:17:35,075
<Default><b>with their
honor on the line</b></Default>

382
00:17:35,099 --> 00:17:37,075
<Default><b>while the masses
cheer them on.</b></Default>

383
00:17:37,099 --> 00:17:38,906
<Default><b>However the
underground arena</b></Default>

384
00:17:38,930 --> 00:17:40,616
<Default><b>is something
entirely different.</b></Default>

385
00:17:40,640 --> 00:17:42,200
<Default><b>No rules down there.</b></Default>

386
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:44,206
<Default><b>You do whatever
it takes to win</b></Default>

387
00:17:44,230 --> 00:17:46,670
<Default><b>but the money to be earned
is much greater.</b></Default>

388
00:17:46,819 --> 00:17:48,819
<Default><b>Bet on a dark
horse and win.</b></Default>

389
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:50,376
<Default><b>Or enter yourself.</b></Default>

390
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:53,040
<Default><b>Either one will get you
the money that you need.</b></Default>

391
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:56,200
<Default><b>Why don't you go
and have a look?</b></Default>

392
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:01,845
<Default><b>[door creaks open]</b></Default>

393
00:18:01,869 --> 00:18:03,949
<Default><b>I know I'm getting
ahead of myself</b></Default>

394
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,515
<Default><b>but I'm already
shivering</b></Default>

395
00:18:05,539 --> 00:18:08,315
<Default><b>just thinking about all the
money you could earn there!</b></Default>

396
00:18:08,339 --> 00:18:15,339
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

397
00:18:22,769 --> 00:18:24,169
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

398
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:36,950
<Default><b>An elephant vs a panda?</b></Default>

399
00:18:37,869 --> 00:18:39,629
<Default><b>You mind if I
stand here?</b></Default>

400
00:18:41,579 --> 00:18:44,500
<Default><b>You're a new face here.
This your first time?</b></Default>

401
00:18:45,329 --> 00:18:47,460
<Default><b>Sasa is gonna win
this one today.</b></Default>

402
00:18:49,339 --> 00:18:50,985
<Default><b>[NADIA]
I mean, Larsazusa</b></Default>

403
00:18:51,009 --> 00:18:52,849
<Default><b>the one you
called a panda.</b></Default>

404
00:18:55,430 --> 00:18:57,509
<Default><b>So then, you
here to bet?</b></Default>

405
00:18:57,599 --> 00:18:59,519
<Default><b>Or are you
entering yourself?</b></Default>

406
00:19:05,190 --> 00:19:06,230
<Default><b>[crack]</b></Default>

407
00:19:08,109 --> 00:19:09,269
<Default><b>[cheering]</b></Default>

408
00:19:09,480 --> 00:19:10,900
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

409
00:19:11,609 --> 00:19:12,769
<Default><b>[cheering]</b></Default>

410
00:19:13,819 --> 00:19:16,740
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
And the winner is Larsazusa!</b></Default>

411
00:19:16,819 --> 00:19:18,459
<Default><b>[NADIA]
What did I say?</b></Default>

412
00:19:19,200 --> 00:19:21,410
<Default><b>That Panda used
some kind of magic.</b></Default>

413
00:19:21,910 --> 00:19:24,345
<Default><b>I guess there really are
no rules down here.</b></Default>

414
00:19:24,369 --> 00:19:25,529
<Default><b>[giggling]</b></Default>

415
00:19:28,089 --> 00:19:29,129
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

416
00:19:32,299 --> 00:19:33,735
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
Up next is Fohl</b></Default>

417
00:19:33,759 --> 00:19:36,509
<Default><b>the little mad dog
of a tiger Demi-human.</b></Default>

418
00:19:36,759 --> 00:19:39,349
<Default><b>Versus the noble scion
and master of the blade</b></Default>

419
00:19:39,430 --> 00:19:41,140
<Default><b>Yuji!</b></Default>

420
00:19:41,430 --> 00:19:43,196
<Default><b>The odds are
in Fohl's favor</b></Default>

421
00:19:43,220 --> 00:19:44,995
<Default><b>but if you think this
silver spooned youth</b></Default>

422
00:19:45,019 --> 00:19:46,116
<Default><b>can tilt the scales</b></Default>

423
00:19:46,140 --> 00:19:48,900
<Default><b>then bet on him
and become rich yourself!</b></Default>

424
00:19:50,559 --> 00:19:53,029
<Default><b>So, you can enter
the arena alone</b></Default>

425
00:19:53,109 --> 00:19:55,216
<Default><b>or in a team
of up to three people.</b></Default>

426
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:56,755
<Default><b>Though between the two</b></Default>

427
00:19:56,779 --> 00:19:58,740
<Default><b>team battles
are more popular.</b></Default>

428
00:19:59,029 --> 00:19:59,869
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

429
00:19:59,950 --> 00:20:02,510
<Default><b>Hey now, you're
quite the drinker, aren't you!</b></Default>

430
00:20:02,539 --> 00:20:03,700
<Default><b>Guess so.</b></Default>

431
00:20:03,789 --> 00:20:05,936
<Default><b>- And?
- [NADIA] And, anything goes.</b></Default>

432
00:20:05,960 --> 00:20:08,000
<Default><b>Sort of like</b></Default>

433
00:20:08,079 --> 00:20:09,679
<Default><b> [shouting]
- [grunts]</b></Default>

434
00:20:11,710 --> 00:20:14,710
<Default><b>[SPECTATOR 01-A (M)] Stop
dodging and fight, white tiger!</b></Default>

435
00:20:15,380 --> 00:20:18,549
<Default><b>My strength comes from my
robust knowledge of the blade.</b></Default>

436
00:20:19,220 --> 00:20:20,759
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

437
00:20:21,140 --> 00:20:22,809
<Default><b>That's enough, okay?</b></Default>

438
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:29,769
<Default><b>Now! Fire Sword!</b></Default>

439
00:20:32,769 --> 00:20:34,169
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

440
00:20:34,779 --> 00:20:36,466
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
And there you have it.</b></Default>

441
00:20:36,490 --> 00:20:38,740
<Default><b>Yuji is the winner!</b></Default>

442
00:20:39,450 --> 00:20:40,505
<Default><b>What a shame.</b></Default>

443
00:20:40,529 --> 00:20:41,966
<Default><b>Don't you feel
sorry for him?</b></Default>

444
00:20:41,990 --> 00:20:43,176
<Default><b>It's only fitting.</b></Default>

445
00:20:43,200 --> 00:20:45,410
<Default><b>After all</b></Default>

446
00:20:45,789 --> 00:20:46,909
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

447
00:20:47,289 --> 00:20:50,039
<Default><b>Well, that's enough
drinking for one day.</b></Default>

448
00:20:51,079 --> 00:20:54,170
<Default><b>Anyways, thanks
for the drinks</b></Default>

449
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:55,410
<Default><b>all right?</b></Default>

450
00:20:56,970 --> 00:20:58,170
<Default><b>[chuckling]</b></Default>

451
00:21:04,809 --> 00:21:07,099
<Default><b>Money is
everything here, huh?</b></Default>

452
00:21:09,099 --> 00:21:11,626
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] I saw
someone from Lurolona Village.</b></Default>

453
00:21:11,650 --> 00:21:13,150
<Default><b>Oh, is that so?</b></Default>

454
00:21:13,519 --> 00:21:15,940
<Default><b>What exactly is it
you're doing, Naofumi?</b></Default>

455
00:21:16,109 --> 00:21:18,005
<Default><b>Getting ready
to enter the fights.</b></Default>

456
00:21:18,029 --> 00:21:18,740
<Default><b>[gasp]</b></Default>

457
00:21:18,819 --> 00:21:20,835
<Default><b>We'll hide our identities
wearing these</b></Default>

458
00:21:20,859 --> 00:21:22,505
<Default><b>and enter
the underground arena.</b></Default>

459
00:21:22,529 --> 00:21:23,545
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

460
00:21:23,569 --> 00:21:26,569
<Default><b>We'll get the prize money
from winning and from the bets.</b></Default>

461
00:21:26,829 --> 00:21:29,789
<Default><b>After, we'll buy the
Demi-humans from Lurolona</b></Default>

462
00:21:29,869 --> 00:21:31,055
<Default><b>that are up for auction.</b></Default>

463
00:21:31,079 --> 00:21:32,976
<Default><b>I didn't understand
anything that you said</b></Default>

464
00:21:33,000 --> 00:21:34,065
<Default><b>but it sounds fun!</b></Default>

465
00:21:34,089 --> 00:21:35,209
<Default><b>[squeals]</b></Default>

466
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,960
<Default><b>Master Naofumi</b></Default>

467
00:21:37,049 --> 00:21:38,969
<Default><b>you're acting
reckless again.</b></Default>

468
00:21:40,380 --> 00:21:41,780
<Default><b>[crowd cheering]</b></Default>

469
00:21:43,430 --> 00:21:44,470
<Default><b>Curses.</b></Default>

470
00:21:44,549 --> 00:21:46,156
<Default><b>They're far too strong.</b></Default>

471
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:47,340
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

472
00:21:47,599 --> 00:21:50,245
<Default><b>We're gonna murder all
three of you where you stand!</b></Default>

473
00:21:50,269 --> 00:21:52,245
<Default><b>[SPECTATOR 01-B (M)] Go for it!
[SPECTATOR 01-B (M)] Kill em!</b></Default>

474
00:21:52,269 --> 00:21:53,456
<Default><b>Excuse me, Master</b></Default>

475
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:55,920
<Default><b>but why do we have
to pretend to be weaker?</b></Default>

476
00:21:56,109 --> 00:21:57,835
<Default><b>It's all in order
to make the audience</b></Default>

477
00:21:57,859 --> 00:22:00,126
<Default><b>think we have no chance
against these guys.</b></Default>

478
00:22:00,150 --> 00:22:01,755
<Default><b>The more of a
dark horse we are</b></Default>

479
00:22:01,779 --> 00:22:03,386
<Default><b>the better the
pay-out will be.</b></Default>

480
00:22:03,410 --> 00:22:05,505
<Default><b>No one told me that
we were horseys.</b></Default>

481
00:22:05,529 --> 00:22:07,409
<Default><b>Okay! Time to
make our move.</b></Default>

482
00:22:07,450 --> 00:22:08,466
<Default><b>Shigaraki!</b></Default>

483
00:22:08,490 --> 00:22:10,810
<Default><b>It sure feels strange
being called that.</b></Default>

484
00:22:18,049 --> 00:22:20,089
<Default><b>Shigaraki!
Humming! Let's go!</b></Default>

485
00:22:20,220 --> 00:22:21,380
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

486
00:22:23,799 --> 00:22:25,140
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

487
00:22:26,220 --> 00:22:27,849
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

488
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:29,220
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

489
00:22:34,769 --> 00:22:35,849
<Default><b>[shouts]</b></Default>

490
00:22:36,190 --> 00:22:37,270
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

491
00:22:39,529 --> 00:22:40,609
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

492
00:22:44,279 --> 00:22:46,200
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

493
00:22:47,779 --> 00:22:48,579
<Default><b>[cheering]</b></Default>

494
00:22:48,660 --> 00:22:50,386
<Default><b>[MC 01-A (M)]
What an upset!</b></Default>

495
00:22:50,410 --> 00:22:53,710
<Default><b>Topak's winning streak has
just been broken by Rockvalley</b></Default>

496
00:22:53,789 --> 00:22:56,539
<Default><b>a brand-new team
in their debut match!</b></Default>

497
00:22:57,130 --> 00:22:58,250
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

498
00:22:59,089 --> 00:23:00,129
<Default><b>We won!</b></Default>

499
00:23:00,170 --> 00:23:02,509
<Default><b>Oh! I thought
we were done for!</b></Default>

500
00:23:02,589 --> 00:23:03,589
<Default><b>Mm.</b></Default>

501
00:23:04,930 --> 00:23:06,090
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

502
00:23:06,549 --> 00:23:09,220
<Default><b>[grunts] Die!</b></Default>

503
00:23:18,190 --> 00:23:21,150
<Default><b>Hell yeah!
Go, Team Rockvalley</b></Default>

504
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:25,216
<Default><b>Looks like
we managed to fool them.</b></Default>

505
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:27,216
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] I feel
a little guilty about it.</b></Default>

506
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:29,200
<Default><b>[FILO]
I love being horseys!</b></Default>

507
00:23:29,329 --> 00:23:33,329
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

